devdoc.title: CollateralTokenAdapter is the adapter that inherited BaseFarmableTokenAdapter. It receives Fathom's ibTOKEN from users and deposit in Fathom's FairLaunch. Hence, users will still earn FATHOM rewards while holding positions.
